---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { actions } from 'astro:actions';
import { getAllPosts } from '../lib/db';

// Obtener posts iniciales para SSR
const posts = getAllPosts();

// Manejar resultados de actions (form POST tradicional)
const createResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsCreate);
const updateResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsUpdate);
const deleteResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsDelete);

// Recargar posts después de cualquier acción exitosa
const currentPosts = (createResult?.data || updateResult?.data || deleteResult?.data)
  ? getAllPosts()
  : posts;
---

<Layout title="Demo CRUD - Múltiples Actions">
  <main>
    <h1>Demo: Múltiples Actions en una Página</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Esta página demuestra cómo usar múltiples actions de Astro con diferentes formularios.
      Cada formulario apunta a una action diferente usando el atributo <code>action</code>.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <!-- ============ FORMULARIO 1: CREAR POST ============ -->
      <section class="card">
        <h2>📝 Crear Nuevo Post</h2>
        <form method="POST" action={actions.postsCreate}>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="create-titulo">Título:</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="create-titulo"
              name="titulo"
              required
              maxlength="100"
              placeholder="Escribe el título..."
            />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="create-contenido">Contenido:</label>
            <textarea
              id="create-contenido"
              name="contenido"
              required
              rows="3"
              placeholder="Escribe el contenido..."
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Crear Post</button>
        </form>

        {createResult?.error && (
          <div class="error">
            Error: {createResult.error.message}
          </div>
        )}
        {createResult?.data && (
          <div class="success">
            ✅ Post creado: "{createResult.data.post.titulo}"
          </div>
        )}
      </section>

      <!-- ============ FORMULARIO 2: EDITAR POST ============ -->
      <section class="card">
        <h2>✏️ Editar Post</h2>
        <form method="POST" action={actions.postsUpdate}>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="edit-id">ID del Post:</label>
            <select id="edit-id" name="id" required>
              <option value="">Selecciona un post...</option>
              {currentPosts.map(post => (
                <option value={post.id}>{post.titulo}</option>
              ))}
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="edit-titulo">Nuevo Título:</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="edit-titulo"
              name="titulo"
              required
              maxlength="100"
              placeholder="Nuevo título..."
            />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="edit-contenido">Nuevo Contenido:</label>
            <textarea
              id="edit-contenido"
              name="contenido"
              required
              rows="3"
              placeholder="Nuevo contenido..."
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-warning">Actualizar Post</button>
        </form>

        {updateResult?.error && (
          <div class="error">
            Error: {updateResult.error.message}
          </div>
        )}
        {updateResult?.data && (
          <div class="success">
            ✅ Post actualizado: "{updateResult.data.post.titulo}"
          </div>
        )}
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ LISTA DE POSTS CON BOTONES DE ELIMINAR ============ -->
    <section class="posts-list">
      <h2>📋 Posts Existentes ({currentPosts.length})</h2>

      {currentPosts.length === 0 ? (
        <p class="empty">No hay posts. ¡Crea uno arriba!</p>
      ) : (
        <div class="posts">
          {currentPosts.map(post => (
            <article class="post-item">
              <div class="post-content">
                <h3>{post.titulo}</h3>
                <p>{post.contenido}</p>
                <small>ID: {post.id}</small>
              </div>

              <!-- FORMULARIO 3: ELIMINAR (uno por cada post) -->
              <form method="POST" action={actions.postsDelete} class="delete-form">
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value={post.id} />
                <button type="submit" class="btn-danger" title="Eliminar post">
                  🗑️ Eliminar
                </button>
              </form>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      )}

      {deleteResult?.error && (
        <div class="error">
          Error al eliminar: {deleteResult.error.message}
        </div>
      )}
      {deleteResult?.data && (
        <div class="success">
          ✅ Post eliminado correctamente
        </div>
      )}
    </section>

    <!-- ============ SECCIÓN EDUCATIVA ============ -->
    <section class="info">
      <h2>💡 ¿Cómo funciona?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Cada <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> tiene su propio <code>action=&#123;actions.postsXXX&#125;</code></li>
        <li>Al enviar, Astro ejecuta la action correspondiente en el servidor</li>
        <li>Usamos <code>Astro.getActionResult()</code> para obtener el resultado</li>
        <li>Los posts se guardan en memoria del servidor (se resetean al reiniciar)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Código clave:</h3>
      <pre><code>{`// En el frontmatter (---)
const createResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsCreate);
const updateResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsUpdate);
const deleteResult = Astro.getActionResult(actions.postsDelete);

// En el HTML
<form method="POST" action={actions.postsCreate}>
<form method="POST" action={actions.postsUpdate}>
<form method="POST" action={actions.postsDelete}>`}</code></pre>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Volver al inicio</a>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .intro {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro code {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .field {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .field label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #555;
  }

  .field input,
  .field textarea,
  .field select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  button {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #0066cc;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #0055aa;
  }

  .btn-warning {
    background: #ff9900;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-warning:hover {
    background: #dd8800;
  }

  .btn-danger {
    background: #dc3545;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-danger:hover {
    background: #bb2d3b;
  }

  .error {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: #ffebee;
    color: #c62828;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .success {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: #e8f5e9;
    color: #2e7d32;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .posts-list {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .posts-list h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .empty {
    color: #888;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .posts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .post-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .post-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .post-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .post-content p {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #666;
  }

  .post-content small {
    color: #999;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .delete-form {
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .info {
    background: #e3f2fd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .info h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #1565c0;
  }

  .info h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .info li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info code {
    background: #bbdefb;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .info pre {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    color: #d4d4d4;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #0066cc;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
